00:14:49,381 --> 00:14:51,781
Sir, what is this scandal you're talking about?

267
00:14:51,781 --> 00:14:55,081
Hey, this has nothing to do with you kids.

268
00:14:55,081 --> 00:14:56,081
See you.

269
00:14:57,781 --> 00:15:00,081
Okay, okay.

270
00:15:00,081 --> 00:15:02,081
Please wait!

271
00:15:02,081 --> 00:15:03,481
That is it?

272
00:15:03,481 --> 00:15:07,581
Mr. Kitajima was a hero for these children.

273
00:15:07,581 --> 00:15:10,581
