280
00:15:31,381 --> 00:15:33,781
that maybe Kitajima had a ghost modeler.

281
00:15:33,781 --> 00:15:35,181
A ghost modeler?

282
00:15:35,181 --> 00:15:38,381
Yeah. His natural landscapes creations

283
00:15:38,381 --> 00:15:41,381
were masterpieces when compared with other modelers.

284
00:15:41,381 --> 00:15:46,681
But it wasn't that he was like that to begin with.

285
00:15:46,681 --> 00:15:50,181
Only, in these past few years he suddenly...

286
00:15:50,181 --> 00:15:51,581
On top of that,

287
00:15:51,581 --> 00:15:55,081
nobody's ever seen him making the figurines in person.

288
00:15:55,081 --> 00:15:56,181
I see.

289
00:15:56,181 --> 00:15:58,881
So, you were hiding in that waiting room

290
00:15:58,881 --> 00:16:00,881
to confirm whether the rumor was true or not?

291
00:16:00,881 --> 00:16:01,881
Yeah.

292
00:16:04,981 --> 00:16:06,581
Right.

293
00:16:06,581 --> 00:16:08,881
It's been bothering me from the start.

294
00:16:08,881 --> 00:16:10,981
Since the time I came to this hall.

295
00:16:13,881 --> 00:16:16,781
Conan, what's the matter?

296
00:16:16,781 --> 00:16:18,681
Could this be it...

297
00:16:18,681 --> 00:16:21,981
Mitsuhiko, doesn't this color look similar

298
00:16:21,981 --> 00:16:25,181
