350
00:18:49,781 --> 00:18:51,981
Then, he tells me...

351
00:18:51,981 --> 00:18:54,081
If so, Morishita...

352
00:18:54,081 --> 00:18:58,381
make my pieces for me too, okay?

353
00:18:58,381 --> 00:19:00,981
Moreover, Mr. Kitajima was preparing

354
00:19:00,981 --> 00:19:03,881
to enter the world tournament with your figurines.

355
00:19:03,881 --> 00:19:06,981
Of course you'd feel bad about it, wouldn't you?

356
00:19:06,981 --> 00:19:09,781
That's why you killed Mr. Kitajima.

357
00:19:09,781 --> 00:19:13,381
No! That, and this case is totally not connected!

358
00:19:13,381 --> 00:19:14,681
However...

359
00:19:14,681 --> 00:19:19,181
