378
00:20:25,681 --> 00:20:30,781
This color was found in your paint case.

379
00:20:30,781 --> 00:20:32,781
Natural light green.

380
00:20:32,781 --> 00:20:35,581
It's used for Masked Yaiba, so I know it!

381
00:20:35,581 --> 00:20:36,981
There's one thing in this room

382
00:20:36,981 --> 00:20:39,981
