383
00:20:39,981 --> 00:20:42,181
Can you tell what is it, everyone?

384
00:20:42,181 --> 00:20:43,581
Over there!

385
00:20:52,681 --> 00:20:54,481
I'm never going to forgive you!

386
00:20:54,481 --> 00:20:56,681
I'll kill you!

387
00:20:56,681 --> 00:20:58,681
Mr. Kitajima said...

388
00:20:58,681 --> 00:21:01,181
that the important thing when making figurines

389
00:21:01,181 --> 00:21:04,681
