390
00:21:04,681 --> 00:21:07,981
That's why you imagined too, didn't you, Mr. Morishita?

391
00:21:07,981 --> 00:21:11,981
When you saw the flowers that Reika brought.

392
00:21:21,481 --> 00:21:22,981
I see.

393
00:21:22,981 --> 00:21:24,381
He painted paint onto the blade to begin with,

394
00:21:24,381 --> 00:21:26,581
