395
00:21:26,581 --> 00:21:29,381
It's all Kitajima's fault!

396
00:21:29,381 --> 00:21:33,381
He asked me to ghost model for him, that's why I...

397
00:21:33,381 --> 00:21:36,781
I'm not to blame!

398
00:23:00,181 --> 00:23:02,581
Everybody complimented us so much.

399
00:23:02,581 --> 00:23:05,181
And, besides, they gave us all these plastic model toys.

400
00:23:05,181 --> 00:23:08,981
All ended well. But...

401
00:23:08,981 --> 00:23:10,581
Okay!

402
00:23:10,581 --> 00:23:12,781
Conan, thanks!

403
00:23:12,781 --> 00:23:15,781
I've already made Yaiba.

404
00:23:15,781 --> 00:23:18,381
After making the plastic model, I'm hungry!

405
00:23:18,381 --> 00:23:19,781
Food! Food!

406
00:23:19,781 --> 00:23:23,281
Hey, come on, make it yourselves!

407
00:23:23,281 --> 00:23:27,281
