411
00:23:35,581 --> 00:23:37,881
Come on!

412
00:23:39,181 --> 00:23:40,281
For you.

413
00:23:41,381 --> 00:23:44,781
Don't open it until I get a hold of all seven of them.

414
00:23:44,781 --> 00:23:46,681
What? Somebody is dead?

